snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 VR Overview Trailer | TGS 2023
snippet.description: Take a look at how Resident Evil 4 has been recreated for PSVR2 in this overview trailer, which explains how interactions and weapons have been completely changed to provide a more immersive experience.
